Class EntityQuery<I,S extends EntityState<I>,B extends EntityQueryBuilder<I,S,B,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.query.EntityQuery<I,S,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of entity identifiers
    S - the type of the entity state
    B - the type of a particular query builder implementation to create the query instances
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Query<I,S>

    public abstract class EntityQuery<I,S extends EntityState<I>,B extends EntityQueryBuilder<I,S,B,?>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A query for the records being the stored Protobuf messages, each declared as a state of an Entity.

    See the package-info.java of this package for more details on usage.
